{"tid":313463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"fb留言尋死 24歲仔大圍站墮橋重傷","createTime":"2017-07-08T10:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T11:26:34.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dba100a90a6b27d67238aade9c7bae552b7d094e","tid":313463,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"港鐵大圍站，下午5時許，一名24歲姓霍男子懷疑由站內一條連接東鐵綫及馬鐵綫的天橋高處墮下，重傷倒卧地面，職員見狀報案。救護員接報趕至，將男事主送往醫院搶救。現場遺下大灘血迹，警方正調查其墮下原因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，霍男早前於fb留言尋死。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56930713&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56930713%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170708&d=1L4Wam1K4R2RMB0Nmhry%2BxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=abdb9f2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56930713%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170708&h=42046115\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56930713&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170708</a>"},{"pid":"c06cce8c26b2dda87842088fed6e872b46f5fdfb","tid":313463,"uid":15977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:54:37.000Z","msg":"咁都死唔去，下次努吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14141e4089c0256e16478f088d6ba0574908d4f3","tid":313463,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/185502_9421ca672f132152954f56f1fe53ab4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F185502_9421ca672f132152954f56f1fe53ab4f.jpg&h=36a1107e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n積屍氣冥界波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f2444afd0cf60